name: Parking Tag Picker
tagline: Unofficial SMS client for Payzone Parking Tags in Dublin City.
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.

_Unofficial Windows Phone application for Payzone Parking Tag in Dublin City:_
>No coins to feed the parking meter? No problem! With the Parking Tag mobile app you can pay for parking using your registered credit >or debit card instead. 
>Parking Tag is a Pay by Phone parking solution which can be used in Dublin City, Dún Laoghaire-Rathdown, Fingal and South Dublin >County Council.

### About
Parking Tag picker was developed as an unofficial app to serve Windows Phone users of Payzone's Parking Tags. 

### Authors and Contributors
@BrianJVarley 

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Parking Tag Picker? Check out our GitHub Repository or [contact support](brianvarley9@gmail.com) and we’ll help you sort it out.
